<mvc:View xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc" 
  xmlns="sap.m" 
  xmlns:fc="ui5lab.fc" 
  xmlns:fci="ui5lab.fc.indicator" 
  displayBlock="true">
  <App>
    <Page enableScrolling="false" 
      showHeader="false">
      <VBox fitContainer="true">
        <fc:CandlestickChart items="{/}" 
          padding="5 20 25 60">
          <fc:layoutData>
            <FlexItemData growFactor="1" minHeight="300px" />
          </fc:layoutData>
          <fc:items>
            <fc:Candle time="{time}" 
              open="{open}" 
              high="{high}" 
              low="{low}" 
              close="{close}"/>
          </fc:items>
        </fc:CandlestickChart>
        <fci:CCIT items="{/}" 
          height="50"
          overboughtZone="20"
          oversoldZone="-20"
          padding="5 20 25 60">
          <fci:layoutData>
            <FlexItemData growFactor="0" minHeight="100px" />
          </fci:layoutData>
          <fci:items>
            <fci:CCITItem time="{time}" 
              y="{= ${close} - ${open}}"/>
          </fci:items>
        </fci:CCIT>
        <fc:LineChart items="{/}" 
          padding="5 20 25 60">
          <fc:layoutData>
            <FlexItemData growFactor="0" minHeight="100px" />
          </fc:layoutData>
          <fc:items>
            <fc:LineChartItem time="{time}" 
              y="{close}"/>
          </fc:items>
        </fc:LineChart>
      </VBox>
    </Page>
  </App>
</mvc:View>
